# GitHub Packages NPM Registry Configuration
# 
# This file configures npm to use GitHub Packages for @hhongli1979-coder scoped packages
# 
# Setup instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to your project root as .npmrc
# 2. Replace YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN with your Personal Access Token
#    - Create token at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
#    - Required scope: read:packages (and write:packages for publishing)
# 
# Security note: Never commit this file with your actual token to version control!
# Add .npmrc to your .gitignore file

@hhongli1979-coder:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN
